---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Now">
	<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8 dark:text-zinc-200">About Me</h1>
		
		<div class="space-y-6 prose prose-sm max-w-none text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-300">
			<section>
				<p>Hi, I'm Parv Mahajan. I'm passionate about technology, artificial intelligence, and their impact on society and education.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 dark:text-zinc-200">Background</h2>
				<p>I'm a computer science enthusiast with a strong interest in understanding how emerging technologies will shape our future. I spend my time learning, building, and writing about these topics.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 dark:text-zinc-200">What I Do</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Write about technology, AI, and career development</li>
					<li>Build web applications and explore new frameworks</li>
					<li>Engage with communities to understand different perspectives on tech</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 dark:text-zinc-200">Interests</h2>
				<p>I'm deeply interested in artificial intelligence, education, web development, and how technology can create positive impact in our world.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 dark:text-zinc-200">This Blog</h2>
				<p>This blog is where I share my thoughts on technology, career transitions, and personal development. Feel free to check out my latest posts and explore different topics.</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</MainLayout>
